#. html
#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/smartstore_activity_deployment.xml:128 /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/smartstore_activity_instance.xml:145
msgid "<p>Each new warm bucket gets uploaded to remote storage. Buckets are only downloaded if they're required for a search and are not already in the local cache. High download rates are a negative indicator of cache health</p>"
msgstr "<p>每個新的逐漸停止使用索引分集皆會上傳至遠端存放區。索引分集僅會在搜尋所需，且尚未存在於本機快取中時下載。高下載速率即為快取健康情況的負面指標。</p>"

#. html
#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/http_event_collector_deployment.xml:612 /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/http_event_collector_instance.env_cloud.xml:555 /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/http_event_collector_instance.xml:554
msgid "<p>Errors due to authentication failure or requests to an incorrect URL are excluded from this chart because they are not associated with any specific token.</p>"
msgstr "<p>此圖表會排除由於驗證失敗或對不正確 URL 的要求之錯誤，因為這些錯誤與特定的 Token 無關。</p>"

#. html
#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/distributed_search_instance.xml:171
msgid "<p>Health Condition indicates the overall status of the peer over the last 10 minutes.</p><p>Peer response times shown are computed over the last 10 minutes. Abnormally high response times (greater than 1000 ms) indicate peer oversubscription. <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.dmc.peerauth\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Splunk help\">Learn More</a></p><p><b>Authentication:</b> the search head requests an authentication token from the peer's /services/admin/auth-tokens endpoint. </p><p><b>Get Bundle List:</b> the search head requests a list of available knowledge bundles from the peer's /services/admin/bundles endpoint. </p><p><b>Get Peer Info:</b> the search head requests instance information from the peer's /services/server/info endpoint. </p>"
msgstr "<p>健康情況會指出過去 10 分鐘內對等的整體狀態。</p><p>顯示的對等回應時間是過去 10 分鐘內的運算結果。異常高的回應時間 (大於 1000 毫秒) 表示對等有過度訂閱的問題。<a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.dmc.peerauth\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Splunk help\">進一步瞭解</a></p><p><b>驗證:</b> 搜尋頭會從對等的 /services/admin/auth-tokens 端點要求驗證 Token。</p><p><b>取得設定包清單:</b> 搜尋頭會從對等的 /services/admin/bundles 端點要求可用知識設定包的清單。</p><p><b>取得對等資訊:</b> 搜尋頭會從對等的 /services/server/info 端點要求執行個體資訊。</p>"

#. html
