msgid "<span class=\"info-message alert alert-info\"><i class=\"icon-alert\"/>You have selected \"index\" from the \"Split By\" menu. If your license peers are running a version of Splunk lower than 6.0, they will not report per index usage and you will see their usage labeled as \"UNKNOWN\".</span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"info-message alert alert-info\"><i class=\"icon-alert\"/>您已選擇 [分割依據] 功能表中的 [索引]。如果您的授權對等節點執行比 Splunk 6.0 更舊的版本，將無法依索引用量進行報告，且您會看到他們的用量標示為 \"UNKNOWN\"。</span>"

